verbose_text: In HBeAg positive patients they reported a strong correlation between HBsAg levels and METAVIR fibrosis scores (r = -0.50, p < 0.001) and HBV DNA levels (r = 0.60, p < 0.001); however, unlike these results, no correlation was observed in HBeAg negative patients (r = 0.09, p = 0.239, r = 0.12, p = 0.123 respectively) [XREF_BIBR].
